   "body" : "Currently, when having the status change of transaction in mempool, bitcoin core will expose the informations of transaction via ZemoMQ.\r\nhttps://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/src/zmq/zmqnotificationinterface.cpp#L160-L195\r\nHaving 3 impact types of the transaction with mempool:\r\n- added.\r\n- blockConnected.\r\n- blockDisconnected.\r\n\r\nInformation about impact type is very important with client that subscribes Zmq channels.\r\nIn some case, we need only information about new transaction accepted to mempool.",
